{"tid":2498465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北辰：若政府堅持消費券逐月發放 將考慮行使基本法賦予之反對預算案權利","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T07:54:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a86558e1b2aaf930ddb393b17d66ba032da39aac","tid":2498465,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"多名議員建議消費券行政安排增加靈活性<br />\n<br />\n多名議員表示，支持政府在經濟低迷下派發消費券，為民紓困，但關注電子消費券的派發方式。實政圓桌田北辰表示，政府不應該分5個月逐次發放1000元，否則會為市民添加太多限制，建議最多分兩期發放，否則他會考慮是否不就預算案投下贊成票。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰認為，政府不應該透過市民消費去「托市」，否則會有額外及沉重的經濟成本，形容「立意不良的政策不會得到好的反應」。多名建制派議員不同意，認為民意支持派發消費券，指政府已經平衡量入為出的公共財政原則。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2388202&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dKZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=450f3307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388202</a>"},{"pid":"192b8287f2503ebda2ed9b52895b1bf1a82abde7","tid":2498465,"uid":161726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"反中亂港"},{"pid":"c5ff279f86242288ff1703513993160abf47b31a","tid":2498465,"uid":47356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:47:46.000Z","msg":"洗定個八月十五啦老坑"},{"pid":"cee39a74e4795a6615567c01537176041b7d7106","tid":2498465,"uid":216163,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"支持田北辰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac46246692332cfe9b97c76ec79759f07e44828","tid":2498465,"uid":61757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"視國安法如無物😱"},{"pid":"9b97e40051c0afae4e0044bcc76f8cbd90933861","tid":2498465,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"仲依賴份歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家係國安法嘅年代"},{"pid":"14855e8975cc